{"tid":381492,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想玩三螢幕應該點升級好","createTime":"2017-08-31T03:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T12:44:59.000Z","uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6f88b12969a7634accf3dd053e67979af7ebbf","tid":381492,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"而家嘅電腦用緊<br />\n老母板 ：asrock h97 killer<br />\nCPU    ：i7-4790（原廠散熱）<br />\nRAM    ：G.Skill 8G DDR3 1600MHz x2<br />\n顯示卡 ：GALAX GTX 980<br />\n<br />\n而家用緊三個頹mon插落一張980度 開nvidia surround<br />\n<br />\n打lol就無問題 一打啲大作例如<br />\nassetto corsa<br />\nforza horizon 3<br />\ngta5 等等<br />\n<br />\n3mon玩就lag到爆炸<br />\n<br />\n應該點升級好<br />\n<br />\n預算5千以內 絕對唔用asus產品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501b0c203c7ba2094b2d58d0cb245fe9cac244dd","tid":381492,"uid":19301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"換display card"},{"pid":"0d76971ed77185ebbddae5ede2b74f2f89e88ad5","tid":381492,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換display card</blockquote><br />\n我都諗左好耐換display card，但係唔知應該換1070，1080定係1080ti"},{"pid":"b959be5801db60e5be970fb2f9750488339da35a","tid":381492,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"Asus有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648df5dcfc890fabcbd1d77fac01fe13d0ad798e","tid":381492,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"換mon / mouse / keyboard"},{"pid":"8db8